title: All Eyes On Sharon Tate (1967)
description:
Info from IMDB:


This short focuses on 'Sharon Tate' at the beginning of her movie career. First we see her attending acting and singing lessons. After several months she is ready to make her first film, Eye of the Devil (1966). We go to the castle in Brive-la-Gaillarde, France, for some filming on location.
